This is a perfect spot to unwind while enjoying delicious food by the river. The atmosphere is relaxing, and the food is both soulful and satisfying.

The menu features some standout dishes that come highly recommended. The Tandoori Prawns and Rawa Fried Mussels are particularly noteworthy, bursting with flavor. The Chicken Handi and Pork Chops also deliver great taste and quality. Additionally, tried other items on the menu, which were all really lovely.
